      <title>印尼钢铁市场困境使 Krakatau 重组复杂化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/indonesian-steel-market-woes-complicate-krakatau-s-restructuring</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印尼钢铁制造商 PT Krakatau Steel 试图重组 15 亿美元的贷款，但其运营和行业困境导致重组过程变得复杂，引发外界关注。]]></description>
