    <item>
      <title>中国现金基金涌入股市 损失数十亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/china-s-cash-funds-lose-billions-in-rush-back-to-stock-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[数十亿美元的资金撤出中国最大的货币市场交易所交易基金，而与此同时，数十亿美元的资金流入跟踪股票的ETF，这表明北京方面终于将持怀疑态度的投资者吸引回了陷入困境的中国股市。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/china-s-cash-funds-lose-billions-in-rush-back-to-stock-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 23:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
