      <title>市场综述：美国就业数据公布前，中东紧张局势导致油价飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中东紧张局势令投资者感到不安，油价上涨，周五晚些时候将公布美国就业数据，该数据将有助于确定未来的利率走势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 22:27:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>因担心以色列可能瞄准伊朗原油，油价继续上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-4</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心以色列可能决定袭击伊朗原油设施以报复本周早些时候的导弹袭击，油价在创下近一年来最大单日涨幅后继续走高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-4</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 22:12:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
